name: Open Source Dashboards UI Kit
description:
This week freebie is a UI kit that you can use to build admin dashboards at the speed of light!


Open Source Dashboards UI Kit includes:

  • 12 ready-made screens with graphs and stats
  • 18 widgets
  • 15 sample dashboard templates
  • Color and typography style guides
  • Ready to use symbols


More details: https://dashboardsdesign.com/
